    "comment": "Rationale: First description of the Munc13-1 knock out mouse using electrophysiology in autistic mouse hippocampal and stratal neurons.\n\nFigure 1 shows a 90% reduction in glutamatergic synaptic transmission. GABAergic transmission id not impaired.\n\nFigure 2 shows that the impaired glutamatergic neurotransmission results from a decrease in the size of the readily releasable vesicle pool, assessed by sucrose application.. Experimental description: Mouse knock-out model; Deletion mutations in the mouse gene for Munc13-1 were\ngenerated by homologous recombination in embryonic stem cells.",
